Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.48,0:00:06.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your mind. Open your mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.36,0:00:22.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Far beyond the deep blue Earth,\nyou and I shall meet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.57,0:00:23.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...as a gentle breeze goes by.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.94,0:00:27.94,AMG TITLE,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,AH! MY GODDESS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.94,0:00:29.41,AMG TITLE,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,AH! MY GODDESS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.41,0:00:36.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A snow-white feather will come\nfluttering down, swaying gently in the air.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.55,0:00:43.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without holding back, I want to\nenvelope you, my one and only love.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.66,0:00:53.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know I have the power to protect\nthe one I love, right here in my hands.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.07,0:00:59.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your mind.\NJust as I've always dreamed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.81,0:01:06.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let the wind carry off\nyour hopes, faraway.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.72,0:01:13.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have wings nobody can see.\NLook, you have them, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.49,0:01:21.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They'll take us to where we can be free.\NAnyone can be free.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.80,0:01:26.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sky is so blue...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.25,0:01:45.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're done!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.56,0:01:50.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it all right if we eat now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.30,0:02:03.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nurse's Office{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.31,0:02:17.77,AMG episode name,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah! What Do Talent and\NHard Work Have to Do With It?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.13,0:02:31.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.10,0:02:34.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.04,0:02:35.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.64,0:02:38.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You've improved greatly, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.44,0:02:41.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Thanks to everyone's hard work!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.61,0:02:44.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to do really well\nthis year, I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.35,0:02:47.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Morisato!\NHere are your lap times.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.88,0:02:51.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,On average, you took a\nwhole second off this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.02,0:02:54.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I guess I have\nyou guys to thank for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.22,0:02:58.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Morisato. No one else has\nimproved as much as you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.89,0:03:03.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Morisato, I'm sure you have a talent\nfor driving. You might be a genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.77,0:03:05.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A genius?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.50,0:03:07.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.20,0:03:10.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, I'm not trying to flatter you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.97,0:03:13.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hasegawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.14,0:03:13.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.88,0:03:15.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.88,0:03:20.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Hasegawa is such a\nhard worker, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.28,0:03:25.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she isn't really the type to stand\nout,\nbut she always gives it her all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.82,0:03:28.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She's a real behind the scenes type,\nI guess you'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.99,0:03:30.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You mean she's a backseat driver?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:31.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Uh, no...{\i0}\NYou mean she's a backseat driver?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.49,0:03:33.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.76,0:03:37.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What? I can't do that!\NThere's no way I can do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.50,0:03:39.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:41.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We already signed you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.50,0:03:43.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.17,0:03:44.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.74,0:03:47.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Morisato, just look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.71,0:03:52.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...a go-kart race,\nfemale drivers only?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:56.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's a new event they're\nintroducing this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.22,0:03:58.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We've decided to participate in the race.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.75,0:04:00.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no way I can do it!{\i0}\NWe've decided to participate in the race.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.99,0:04:03.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's no ''no way'' about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.03,0:04:06.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only female member we have.\NWe don't have any choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.53,0:04:08.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you give it a shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.23,0:04:10.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I think Keiichi's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.03,0:04:11.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.59,0:04:12.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.83,0:04:17.31,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's not going to be a tough race,\nsince all the drivers will be girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.31,0:04:19.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's not going to work out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.57,0:04:22.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's absolutely no way\nthat I can race!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.21,0:04:23.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.51,0:04:26.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I just know it! I know I can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:33.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, you do know how to\ndrive a regular car, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.42,0:04:34.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:36.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.43,0:04:39.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It'll seem like you're going really\nfast at first, but you'll realize...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:41.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...you have nothing to fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.06,0:04:42.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But still!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.33,0:04:45.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A man's gotta have balls! Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:47.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I'm a woman...{\i0}\NA man's gotta have balls! Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:54.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Too...too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.91,0:04:59.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,O Spirit who exists in the Valley of Air...\NO Spirit who arrives with the Wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.58,0:05:01.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Air Bug Spiralee!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.45,0:05:03.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stifle that vehicle's power!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.23,0:05:14.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The engine shut down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.80,0:05:16.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Great, she got lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.84,0:05:21.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Hasegawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:26.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you afraid of riding this go-kart?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.37,0:05:27.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terrified!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.81,0:05:31.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that I'm ever going\nto be able to drive that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.45,0:05:35.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right, looks like\nit's still intact, Den-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.11,0:05:38.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't know if we can\nkeep it running until the race.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.82,0:05:41.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And we can't have\NHasegawa getting hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:44.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I think you're right about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.96,0:05:46.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.30,0:05:49.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm certain that she'll\nbe able to drive that kart!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.93,0:05:50.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.33,0:05:53.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.03,0:05:56.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please, will you let me\ntake care of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.78,0:06:09.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have an extra person living here\na while, so make her feel welcome, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.92,0:06:11.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Boot camp, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.52,0:06:15.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess it's just like Belldandy\nto come up with something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.09,0:06:19.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops! I forgot to turn off Banpei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.46,0:06:20.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.10,0:06:25.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What...what in the world is this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.31,0:06:40.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.02,0:06:41.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.48,0:06:46.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine, I'm fine! I'm just a\nlittle out of breath, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.92,0:06:50.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But anyway, that robot you made is\nvery impressive! It's really amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.93,0:06:52.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He is, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.83,0:06:56.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you can tell how awesome my Banpei\nis, you're amazing yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.23,0:06:58.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, let's not get carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.13,0:06:59.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.37,0:07:03.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! You're here to train, aren't you?\NThen I'm going to help you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:05.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.52,0:07:17.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know you had something\nlike this right in your backyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.55,0:07:20.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, this is the first time\nI've ever seen it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.29,0:07:21.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Only one person would do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.86,0:07:23.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I made it!{\i0}\NOnly one person would do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.69,0:07:28.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I call it the Tariki Hongan Temple\NRace Circuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.49,0:07:30.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's a super-tight curve\nat the first corner!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.90,0:07:33.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to time your deceleration\nand acceleration perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.74,0:07:36.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Once you're through\nan S-shaped chicane...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.47,0:07:38.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll hit a backstraight running!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.71,0:07:41.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You'll exploit the full potential\nof your machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.41,0:07:45.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And once you clear the last hill,\nit's just a straightaway to the finish line.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.85,0:07:48.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Brilliant, wouldn't you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.12,0:07:51.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Um, we're just borrowing\nthis place, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.05,0:07:53.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind the little details!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.09,0:07:54.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Time to practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:58.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you can just master this course\nof mine, you'll have nothing to fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.26,0:08:01.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't do it!\nIt's beyond me, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.26,0:08:03.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.37,0:08:08.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My Voice-controlled Device,\nthe ''Aye-Aye-Sir'' No. 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.97,0:08:11.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell him what to do\nand he'll drive for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.84,0:08:13.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.98,0:08:16.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.38,0:08:17.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.71,0:08:20.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, what I meant was slow down!\NStop, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:22.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.82,0:08:29.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You should've just\nlet me take care of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.22,0:08:32.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, as if you could\never get it right, Urd!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.26,0:08:33.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wanna bet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:37.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da! Industrial-strength\NJekyll & Hyde 500!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.33,0:08:38.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.40,0:08:41.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is, she's way too timid,\nand that's what we've got to fix!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.77,0:08:43.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This will reverse her personality!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:47.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, she'll\nbecome super-aggressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.04,0:08:50.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hasegawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.98,0:08:53.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you shut up? Get off my case!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.82,0:08:55.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Man, what a drag...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.95,0:08:58.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That potion reversed her\ndiligent nature as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:09:01.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and turned her into a total slacker!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:03.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you couldn't handle it, Urd!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.43,0:09:07.73,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It was just a little too strong for her.\nI'll just neutralize it with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.73,0:09:09.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Morisato!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.43,0:09:13.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go out now, so get all\nthe shopping done before I come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.60,0:09:14.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Dai-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.50,0:09:17.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Was that Tamiya just now?{\i0}\NLet's go, Dai-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.21,0:09:22.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it is supposed to turn her into\nthe person who resembles her the least.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.38,0:09:23.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.86,0:09:40.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's the problem, Hasegawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.36,0:09:42.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.33,0:09:45.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never be able to\ngo fast like you, Morisato!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.40,0:09:47.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hasegawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.03,0:09:50.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't have the\ntalent for this, you see!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.21,0:09:51.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Neither do I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.47,0:09:55.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you do. Look how fast\nyou can make that kart go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.14,0:09:58.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many times I try,\nI'm still scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.78,0:10:03.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I'm just as scared as you.\NHow can it not be scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.19,0:10:14.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's call it a day, then.\NWhy don't you go wash your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.03,0:10:15.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.53,0:10:17.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.43,0:10:22.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right, that should make it better.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.54,0:10:24.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.75,0:10:34.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's just no way that I can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.32,0:10:38.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Here you all are, trying to help me out,\nand I'm still not getting better.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.12,0:10:40.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I just keep messing up...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.18,0:10:41.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I know you can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.89,0:10:44.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How in the world can you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.13,0:10:48.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've tried and tried with all my might\nand I've never once succeeded!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.40,0:10:50.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.13,0:10:51.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is true!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.04,0:10:57.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Hasegawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.15,0:11:11.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:14.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow I'll see to it that\nyou do better, I promise you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.99,0:11:15.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.79,0:11:16.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, come on!{\i0}\NNot gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.62,0:11:18.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,As if you didn't mess up yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.49,0:11:19.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Did I, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.26,0:11:22.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.93,0:11:23.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yuck...{\i0}\NWhat's the big idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.67,0:11:29.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What is this slimy stuff\nthat's sticking to my tongue?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.90,0:11:32.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I'm the one who made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.87,0:11:33.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.51,0:11:39.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've been a terrible cook\nsince I was a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.35,0:11:42.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They used to call me\nthe Homicidal Chef...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.28,0:11:47.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My teacher put ''Please have Sora\npractice cooking'' on my report card.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.92,0:11:51.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then please\nlet me make dinner tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.25,0:11:54.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That way, I can show you once and\nfor all that no matter what I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.96,0:11:57.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm bound to fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.43,0:12:02.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Hasegawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.00,0:12:04.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I went through intense training.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.97,0:12:09.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I had my mom teach me at home,\nand I practiced everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.14,0:12:13.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter what I do,\nI always fail. So please...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.57,0:12:15.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,One more time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.75,0:12:22.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try it one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.06,0:12:26.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,One more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.17,0:12:34.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right, please get on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.54,0:12:37.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Um, where am I supposed to sit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.53,0:12:38.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.94,0:12:39.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.90,0:12:41.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.11,0:12:45.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right, we're off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.08,0:12:46.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Careful, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.72,0:12:58.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's scary...it's scary after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.66,0:13:01.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just because we're riding double doesn't\nmake it any less terrifying!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.93,0:13:03.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A skylark.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.95,0:13:23.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you're looking down at the ground,\nyou'll lose sight of what's around you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.59,0:13:26.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...that's what makes it seem even scarier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.29,0:13:34.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look straight ahead and feel the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.40,0:13:38.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And little by little,\nstart talking to your machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.37,0:13:41.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look straight ahead...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.11,0:13:51.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look straight ahead...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.38,0:13:54.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...feel the wind...and...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:57.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...start talking to your machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.96,0:14:10.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is it all right if ride you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.50,0:14:15.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I'm good enough to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.71,0:14:24.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.53,0:15:21.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Here she comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.74,0:15:24.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right! She completed the course!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.54,0:15:28.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, Hasegawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.68,0:15:30.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, Morisato.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.78,0:15:33.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You see? You can do anything if you try.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.55,0:15:36.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act like such a hotshot when\neverything you did was useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.78,0:15:38.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.15,0:15:39.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You wanna fight?{\i0}\NWhat did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.65,0:15:41.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You little...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:45.73,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Here's to the end of training camp\nand Hasegawa's great achievements...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.73,0:15:47.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.23,0:15:49.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.96,0:15:51.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.83,0:15:52.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:54.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I made that, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.94,0:15:57.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Really, it's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.54,0:16:00.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All your hard training\npaid off, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.91,0:16:01.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.74,0:16:04.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now all you have to do is\nto come in first tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.88,0:16:05.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.31,0:16:08.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.95,0:16:14.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why are you all spaced out?\NYou know you're gonna win for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.64,0:16:34.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.48,0:16:38.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Hasegawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.98,0:16:40.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Hasegawa...um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.95,0:16:44.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm all right. I admit\nI'm still a little anxious, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.29,0:16:49.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...since you all did so much to help me\nget this far, I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.26,0:16:52.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I really appreciate all your support.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.62,0:16:55.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then, good night!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.51,0:17:08.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to be all right...\nthis time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.15,0:17:17.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be all right...this time, for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.03,0:17:25.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Hasegawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:33.73,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ready, set...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.27,0:17:36.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right, we're set.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.10,0:17:37.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Hasegawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.91,0:17:41.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's holding her up?\NShe's going to be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.61,0:17:45.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Hasegawa, are you ready to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.38,0:17:46.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.25,0:17:49.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Hasegawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.15,0:17:50.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Hasegawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:53.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I got a stomachache all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.22,0:17:56.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! We have to get you\nto the doctor right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.46,0:18:00.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, I think I'll be fine\nif I just lie down a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.06,0:18:01.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.77,0:18:15.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What? Does that mean\nshe's not going to be in the race?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.81,0:18:18.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,After all that training, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.57,0:18:22.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a stomachache,\nshe's got to psyche herself out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.17,0:18:24.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to ask a favor of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.39,0:18:29.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Would you please wait, just a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.40,0:18:43.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Hasegawa, I've brought you\nsome rice gruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.08,0:18:55.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.92,0:18:57.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.52,0:19:03.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When I was in grammar school,\nI practiced hard to learn how to cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.12,0:19:08.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to make everyone else look\nbad at a presentation in home ec class.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.30,0:19:14.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I practiced and practiced and\nmy friends all cheered me on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.67,0:19:17.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And I did get a lot better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:20.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My cooking started to\ntaste a little better too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.03,0:19:21.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.39,0:19:39.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You feigned...your illness?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.56,0:19:40.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.93,0:19:45.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I practiced so hard,\nI was so scared that I might fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.74,0:19:57.24,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,While I was resting in the nurse's office,\ntears started rolling down my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.24,0:20:02.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was so frustrated, and so embarrassed.\nI was so ashamed of myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.25,0:20:07.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I decided then and there that\nI'd never pull a stunt like that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.02,0:20:08.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.22,0:20:09.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.96,0:20:12.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm still scared, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.13,0:20:16.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever I think that I might fail,\nit scares me so much I can't even move!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.60,0:20:23.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is who you are right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.17,0:20:25.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please, give her all of your support.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.47,0:20:27.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please believe in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.74,0:20:30.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You've done so much\nto get to this point!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.77,0:20:32.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.45,0:20:34.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But, Belldandy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.02,0:20:36.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We all get scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.51,0:20:39.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But you never want to betray yourself,\nso you have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.99,0:20:44.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...believe in all that you've accomplished,\nand try to overcome that fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.39,0:20:48.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you suppose Keiichi was\nable to improve his lap time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.06,0:20:49.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.20,0:20:53.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not because of his talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.63,0:20:59.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But because he's trained so hard\nto overcome his fear and insecurities.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.09,0:21:00.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A genius?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.01,0:21:02.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't think so!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.98,0:21:07.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Look, I'm just as scared as you.\NHow can it not be scary{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.99,0:21:19.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you're looking down at the ground,\nyou'll lose sight of what's around you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.33,0:21:21.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...that's what makes it seem even scarier.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.02,0:21:45.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Morisato...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.19,0:21:47.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.36,0:21:51.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You've got one hour\nbefore the race starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.99,0:21:54.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Morisato!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.60,0:21:58.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.64,0:22:13.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to look down\nat the ground anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.99,0:22:29.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Always believe in yourself and your\NDreams. You have a Wing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.13,0:22:35.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I love you so much it hurts...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.14,0:22:40.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And it hurts me that\nI can't tell you how I feel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.81,0:22:45.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You and I have matching hearts...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.85,0:22:50.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So we must share the\nsame scars deep down inside.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.99,0:22:56.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But now that I'm in your arms,\nI think I can catch...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.42,0:23:01.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...your pounding heartbeat this time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.39,0:23:06.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nobody else matters...\NAll we have to do is gaze at each other.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.90,0:23:12.31,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's all right for your heart to flutter...\NAll we have to do is love each other.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.31,0:23:17.31,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your heart, and\nride that favorable wind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.31,0:23:22.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't run away from happiness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.45,0:23:28.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll always be waiting for you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.36,0:23:33.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So come rest your wings anytime.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.56,0:23:38.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's all right to cry...\nanytime you need to.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.57,0:23:44.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just want to see you again...\NAll we have to do is love each other.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.21,0:23:49.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your heart, and\nride that favorable wind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.18,0:23:54.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just want you to be happy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.98,0:23:59.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The sea...it is both the source of life,\nand a place to rest your soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.75,0:24:03.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Embraced by Nature, the goddesses\nbare their minds and souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.29,0:24:06.76,AMG episode name,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode:\NAh! Confess Your Love Under the Moon?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.76,0:24:10.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Megumi, just watch\nthis brave act of mine!
